Length\">Length</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns the known size of the remaining data.\nReturns `some (.fixed n)` with the current byte count, or `some (.fixed 0)` if the body has\nalready been consumed or closed.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Body/Full.html#Std.Http.Body.Full.getKnownSize","kind":"def","line":92,"name":"Std.Http.Body.Full.getKnownSize","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Std/Http/Data/Body/Full.lean#L92-L101"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Body/Full.html#Std.Http.Body.Full.isClosed\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Body</span>.<span class=\"name\">Full</span>.<span class=\"name\">isClosed</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">full</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Body/Full.html#Std.Http.Body.Full\">Full</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Async/Basic.html#Std.Async.Async\">Async.Async</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` when the data has been consumed or the body has been closed.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Body/Full.html#Std.Http.Body.Full.isClosed","kind":"def","line":85,"name":"Std.Http.Body.Full.isClosed","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Std/Http/Data/Body/Full.lean#L85-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Body/Full.html#Std.Http.Body.Full.close\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Body</span>.<span class=\"name\">Full</span>.<span class=\"name\">close</span></a><